articles.title: Missiles target Kyiv as visiting African leaders push Ukraine and Russia for peace and grain - The Associated Press
African peace mission visits Ukrainian capital to sounds of air raid - Reuters
articles.description: At least two explosions rocked Kyiv on Friday and air raid sirens blared as African leaders began a peace mission, hoping to mediate between Ukraine and Russia.
articles.content:
